thread.title: Andrew Goldsmith
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Andrew Goldsmith

author: Andrew Goldsmith
title: Andrew Goldsmith
text: Dealing with Ink Station is very easy. Ordering process and speed of delivery is perfect. My only reservation at this stage is the quality of the toner refills which may be a function of the hardware hungry printer, or a function of the poor yield from the cartridge. Probably unlikely I will ever be able test this to any definitive degree but I do seem to consume cartridges much faster than previous. Cheers
